<section class="section">
    <div class="r-container">
        <div class="d-flex flex-lg-row flex-column-reverse gap-3">
            <div class="col col-lg-12">
                <div class="d-flex flex-column gap-3">
                    
                    <p>
                        Our Domiciliary Care service provides individuals with the support they need to continue living independently in their own homes. Many people prefer the comfort and familiarity of home, and with the right level of care, it is possible to enjoy safety, dignity, and a high quality of life without the need to move into a residential setting. Our care is flexible, personalised, and designed to adapt as needs change, ensuring that each person receives the right support at the right time.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        We begin with a detailed assessment to understand daily routines, health requirements, personal preferences, and the outcomes that matter to the individual. Based on this, we create a tailored plan that supports independence while providing reassurance and professional oversight. Visits can be arranged from a few hours a week to several times a day, depending on what is needed.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Our carers assist with washing, dressing, grooming, medication prompts, meals, hydration, and mobility. They also help with household tasks such as cleaning, laundry, and shopping to ensure a safe and comfortable living environment. Beyond practical support, companionship is an important part of this service. Carers offer conversation, emotional support, and encouragement, helping individuals stay connected, confident, and engaged in their daily lives.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Regular reviews ensure that care remains aligned with current needs, and we work closely with health professionals when required. Whether someone is recovering from illness, managing a long term condition, or simply needs a little extra help at home, our Domiciliary Care service provides respectful and reliable support that promotes wellbeing and independence.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Our aim is to help individuals remain in the place they know and love, while receiving compassionate care that upholds dignity and enhances daily life. With the right support in place, people can continue to enjoy their routines, their relationships, and the comfort of familiar surroundings.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
